resources.string: Ho Chi Minh city National University

Along with the process of international economic integration, the need to learn and advise on legal issues in English for organizations and individuals in society is becoming more and more popular. In order to help law students develop their professional knowledge, improve their English skills, step by step build up their capacity to research legal issues related to international economic integration, The Youth Union of University of Economics and Laws VNU-HCM synthesizes legal terms in Vietnamese and English to produce "Dictionary of Vietnamese - English legal terminology".
